int p, r, t, Ret[N], _Ret[N], Acq[N][N], _Acq[N][N], P[M], R[M], q[N], Ok[N];
bool Flag[N][N], Inq[N];

inline bool Check(int k)
{
	for (int i = 1; i <= r; i ++)
		Ret[i] = _Ret[i];
	for (int i = 1; i <= p; i ++)
		for (int j = 1; j <= r; j ++)
			Acq[i][j] = _Acq[i][j];
	for (int i = 1; i <= k; i ++)
	{
		Acq[P[i]][R[i]] --;
		Ret[R[i]] --;
	}
	int _l = 1, _r = 0;
	for (int i = 1; i <= p; i ++)
	{
		Ok[i] = Inq[i] = 0;
		for (int j = 1; j <= r; j ++)
		{
			Flag[i][j] = (Ret[j] >= Acq[i][j]);
			Ok[i] += Flag[i][j];
		}
		if (Ok[i] == r) q[++ _r] = i, Inq[i] = 1;
	}
	while (_l <= _r)
	{
		int z = q[_l ++];
		for (int i = 1; i <= r; i ++)
			Ret[i] += _Acq[z][i] - Acq[z][i];
		for (int i = 1; i <= p; i ++)
		{
			if (Inq[i]) continue ;
			for (int j = 1; j <= r; j ++)
				if (!Flag[i][j] && Ret[j] >= Acq[i][j])
				{
					Flag[i][j] = 1;
					Ok[i] ++;
				}
			if (Ok[i] == r) q[++ _r] = i, Inq[i] = 1;
		}
	}
	return _r == p;
}

int main()
{
	scanf("%d%d%d", &p, &r, &t);
	for (int i = 1; i <= r; i ++)
	{
		scanf("%d", Ret + i);
		_Ret[i] = Ret[i];
	}
	for (int i = 1; i <= p; i ++)
		for (int j = 1; j <= r; j ++)
		{
			scanf("%d", Acq[i] + j);
			_Acq[i][j] = Acq[i][j];
		}
	for (int i = 1; i <= t; i ++)
		scanf("%d%d", P + i, R + i);
	int _l = 0, _r = t + 1;
	while (_l < _r)
	{
		int mid = (_l + _r) >> 1;
		if (Check(mid)) _l = mid + 1;
			else _r = mid;
	}
	if (_l == t + 1) puts("-1");
		else printf("%d\n", _l);
	return 0;
}

#include <bits/stdc++.h>

#define FI(i,a,b) for(int i=(a);i<=(b);i++)
#define FD(i,a,b) for(int i=(a);i>=(b);i--)

using namespace std;

int n, re, T, ini[305], need[305][305];
int acq[200005][2];

int cur[305], cneed[305][305];
bool done[305];

bool ok(int til){
	FI(i, 1, re) cur[i] = ini[i];
	FI(i, 1, n) FI(j, 1, re) cneed[i][j] = need[i][j];
	FI(i, 1, til){
		cur[acq[i][1]]--;
		cneed[acq[i][0]][acq[i][1]]--;
	}
	FI(i, 1, n) done[i] = false;
	//can avoid death?
	int cnt = 0;
	while(cnt < n){
		bool lock = true;
		FI(i, 1, n) if(!done[i]){
			bool feasible = true;
			FI(j, 1, re) if(cneed[i][j] > cur[j]){
				feasible = false;
				break;
			}
			if(feasible){
				done[i] = true;
				lock = false;
				cnt++;
				FI(j, 1, re) cur[j] += need[i][j] - cneed[i][j];
			}
		}
		if(lock) return false;
	}
	return true;
}

int main(){
	scanf("%d %d %d", &n, &re, &T);
	FI(i, 1, re) scanf("%d", &ini[i]);
	FI(i, 1, n) FI(j, 1, re) scanf("%d", &need[i][j]);
	FI(i, 1, T) scanf("%d %d", &acq[i][0], &acq[i][1]);
	int l = 0, r = T + 1;
	while(r - l > 1){
		int m = (l + r) >> 1;
		if(ok(m)) l = m;
		else r = m;
	}
	if(r == T + 1) r = -1;
	printf("%d\n", r);
	return 0;
}

